title: Bobby Goes To A Relationship Therapist + Ronnie Dunn Stops By With A Huge Announcement + Amy Sees Major Drama On An Airplane
itunes:title: Bobby Goes To A Relationship Therapist + Ronnie Dunn Stops By With A Huge Announcement + Amy Sees Major Drama On An Airplane
description:
Bobby talks about his first appointment with his therapist, who is actually meant for couples. Ronnie Dunn of Brooks and Dunn stops by to make a big announcement and talk about what he does for fun. Amy saw some crazy drama on an airplane between two people over a credit card.
